Package: prefab
Title: Opinionated Project Scaffolding via Composable Themes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Ben",
             family = "Zipperer",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "benzipperer@gmail.com"),
      person(given = "Economic Policy Institute",
             role = c("cph", "fnd")))
Description: Provides a composable theme system for project scaffolding. Themes
    are ordered lists of steps that deploy files, inline text, or execute
    functions, with per-file merge strategies for handling pre-existing content.
    Includes pre-set themes for R analysis projects, targets workflows, and
    Claude Code agent configuration.
